			<h3><span><a class="sharelink" rel="nofollow" href="#p5686" onclick="return false;">Поделиться</a><strong>30</strong><a class="permalink" rel="nofollow" href="http://lilitochka.ru/viewtopic.php?id=181&amp;p=2#p5686">2009-07-01 11:48:29</a></span></h3>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="post-author">
					<ul>
						<li class="pa-author"><span class="acchide">Автор:&nbsp;</span>Laura</li>
						<li class="pa-title">Гость</li>
